<view class="home">
  <view class="welcome-card" style="{{welcomeStyle}}">
    <view class="welcome-title">欢迎回来，{{welcomeName}}</view>
    <view class="welcome-subtitle">佳慧记账已为您准备好各模块的快捷入口</view>
  </view>

  <view class="grid">
    <view
      class="tile"
      wx:for="{{tiles}}"
      wx:key="key"
      style="{{item.background}}"
      data-url="{{item.url}}"
      data-type="{{item.type}}"
      bindtap="onTileTap"
    >
      <view class="tile-icon" style="background-color: {{tileIconColor}}; -webkit-mask-image: url({{item.icon}}); mask-image: url({{item.icon}});"></view>
      <text class="tile-label">{{item.label}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice-card" style="{{noticeStyle}}">
    <text class="notice-title">注意：</text>
    <text class="notice-text">系统默认将老挝币（LAK）金额按照“万”为单位展示，请录入与核对时留意换算。</text>
  </view>
</view>
